{"tid":2354930,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普簽行政命令禁支付寶等多個中國應用程式交易","createTime":"2021-01-06T00:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T08:21:24.000Z","uid":141151,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"656d9a2cd1e010c3ef4f01cffab671b72f2f6977","tid":2354930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:14:31.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽行政命令禁支付寶等多個中國應用程式交易<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568853-20210106.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568853-20210106.htm&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG426uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=207c6be3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568853-20210106.htm&h=7be27cf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568853-20210106.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普簽署行政命令，禁止與碼蟻集團旗下支付寶等中國應用程式進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報道，被禁的8個中國應用程式，包括支付寶、QQ錢包和微信支付等，行政命令要求商務部，確定哪些交易將被禁止。<br />\n<br />\n官員說，中國應用程式擁有龐大的用戶群，有機會讀取敏感數據，做法是要遏止程式對美國人構成的威脅。商務部有45天時間採取行動，但當局計劃在特朗普今個月20日卸任前，識別出需要禁止的交易。"},{"pid":"ab714d6ef755178a7696e32b31b7b1b39d84c26f","tid":2354930,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:15:31.000Z","msg":"係咪真係禁到？得返十幾日"},{"pid":"93b7759c7e44947ceeb17e7896177bc8878e3bb7","tid":2354930,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8de110a7b66eb598d19c8ec7bc2cdb32e6a559","tid":2354930,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cac88bcfb723dbde5f0e9f7130f6352c256247","tid":2354930,"uid":17443,"like":0,"di